j\fi180\ri0\li0{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj}{Membership beginning in 2023 and effect on incumbent senators; vacancies prior to 2023; see }\par}{\pard\plain\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0\cf5{{\f5\fs12\hyphpar0\qj\cf5{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://www.legis.iowa.gov/docs/acts/2021/CH2.pdf" }{\fldrslt \cf5 \f5 \fs12{{2021 Acts, 2nd Ex, ch 2, \'a73, 4}}}}}}\par}}